  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "What are the steps to put my car in Ola Cab services?",
  "response": "To list your car on **Ola Cabs** as a driver-partner, you need to follow these steps:\n\n### **Step 1: Check Eligibility**\nBefore applying, ensure you meet the following criteria:\n1. **Car Requirements**:\n   - The car should be in good condition.\n   - It should be **less than 5 years old** (varies by city).\n   - It should have a **valid Registration Certificate (RC)**.\n   - Insurance and Pollution Under Control (PUC) certificate must be valid.\n   - The previous 6 months\u2019 **No Objection Certificate (NOC)** is required if the car is financed.\n2. **Driver Requirements**:\n   - You must be **at least 18\u201321 years old** (depending on the region).\n   - You should have a **valid driving license**.\n   - A **background check** is mandatory in some regions.\n\n### **Step 2: Register Online**\n1. Visit the **Ola Driver Partner** website or download the **Ola Driver app** from the Google Play Store or Apple App Store.\n2. Create an account using your **mobile number** and fill in the required details (name, address, etc.).\n3. Upload the necessary documents:\n   - Driving license\n   - Car RC book\n   - Car insurance\n   - PUC certificate\n   - PAN card (optional, but recommended)\n   - Bank account details (for payments)\n\n### **Step 3: Vehicle Inspection**\n1. Ola will schedule a **vehicle inspection** after you submit your application.\n2. A representative will inspect your car for eligibility and ensure it meets Ola\u2019s standards.\n\n### **Step 4: Complete Training (if required)**\n1. You may need to attend a **short training session** conducted by Ola to understand the app, customer service, and safety guidelines.\n\n### **Step 5: Verification and Approval**\n1. Ola will verify your documents and car details.\n2. Once approved, you will be notified to start accepting rides.\n\n### **Step 6: Start Earning**\n1. Log in to the **Ola Driver app**, go online, and start accepting ride requests.\n2. You\u2019ll earn based on the distance traveled and time spent on trips.\n\n### **Additional Notes**:\n- Ola charges a **commission** on each ride.\n- Ensure your car is clean and well-maintained to avoid penalties.\n- You can also opt for **Ola Rentals** or **Outstation trips** for additional earning opportunities.\n\nIf you face any issues during the registration process, contact Ola\u2019s support team for assistance.",
  "temperature": 1.0,
